WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.279 --> 00:00:10.000
Fun bridal shower ideas are hard to come by.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.260
Why not throw a shower for gifts that will
be both sentimental and practical?

00:00:15.260 --> 00:00:21.680
If you or a friend is a bride who is considering
using the very popular brooch bouquet for

00:00:21.680 --> 00:00:25.279
your wedding, here is an idea for you.

00:00:25.279 --> 00:00:30.759
Have each guest bring a sparkly beautiful
brooch along with a themed shower gift.

00:00:30.759 --> 00:00:35.879
This way you can incorporate all the brooches
you get for your shower and have one from

00:00:35.879 --> 00:00:41.329
all of your closest family and friends to
carry with you on your wedding day in your

00:00:41.329 --> 00:00:43.100
gorgeous bridal bouquet.

00:00:43.100 --> 00:00:48.769
The best part about a brooch bouquet is that
it will not parish like fresh flowers, and

00:00:48.769 --> 00:00:53.059
you can even pass it down for future generations
to use.

00:00:53.059 --> 00:00:59.390
I love the idea of mixing both flowers and
brooches so you can have the best of both

00:00:59.390 --> 00:01:00.680
worlds!

00:01:00.680 --> 00:01:05.910
This will also make it easy for your guests
as they will know just what to shop for and

00:01:05.910 --> 00:01:07.890
buy you for your bridal shower.

00:01:07.890 --> 00:01:12.619
They may even contribute an heirloom brooch
from some of your family members from long

00:01:12.619 --> 00:01:17.570
ago which would make your bouquet even more
special!

00:01:17.570 --> 00:01:23.229
Pinterest is such a great source of ideas
for unique brooch bouquets.

00:01:23.229 --> 00:01:27.520
You can even choose to have a particular color
or style.

00:01:27.520 --> 00:01:32.520
Many brooch bouquets are primarily either
pearl or pearl and rhinestone.

00:01:32.520 --> 00:01:38.960
Don't be afraid to mix it up and make yours
uniquely tailored to your tastes!

00:01:38.960 --> 00:01:44.810
